menu "Board Support Package (BSP)"

    config BSP_I2C_CLOCK_SPEED_HZ
        int "I2C Clock Speed (Hz)"
        default 400000
        range 100000 1000000
        help
            I2C bus clock speed in Hz.
            
            Common values:
            - 100000 (100kHz) - Standard mode
            - 400000 (400kHz) - Fast mode (recommended)
            - 1000000 (1MHz) - Fast mode plus (if supported)
            
            Note: Higher speeds may not work with all I2C devices.
            Check your hardware specifications before changing.

endmenu
